    ("Reef-building (hermatypic) corals host symbiotic:", ["bacteria only", "zooxanthellae (photosynthetic dinoflagellates)", "sponges", "tube worms"], 1, "Zooxanthellae provide up to 90% of the coral's energy."),
    ("Coral polyps secrete:", ["silica shells", "calcium carbonate skeletons", "chitin exoskeletons", "cellulose walls"], 1, "CaCO₃ skeletons build the reef structure."),
